{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Don't scrap funding for BTEC Performing Arts",
        "additional_details": "I want the government to reconsider defunding the subject BTEC Performing Arts. I studied BTEC Performing Arts at school and I loved the subject as did many others. It can lead to many 'sustainable jobs and careers'. I wonder how many people in TV shows they like to watch took this subject at school. The arts is a big part of entertainment yet the government continues to disregard it. Please do not defund this much loved subject!",
        "background": "I want the government to not defund BTEC Performing Arts. The government states \u2018that all technical qualifications should offer the firm prospect of a sustainable job and career.\u2019 So they don't think that Performing Arts can lead to a good career! Well it can!!",
